    <briefdescription>
<para>XPointer framework and schemes. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>API to evaluate XPointer expressions. The following schemes are supported:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>element()</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>xmlns()</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>xpath1()</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>xpointer() is an alias for the xpath1() scheme. The point and range extensions are not supported.</para>
